generatedPrompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon watercolor of a slightly frazzled, very fluffy gray cat attempting to balance a precarious stack of colorful, lopsided birthday gifts. One paw is outstretched for balance, and it has a wide-eyed, comical expression of intense concentration. A single, tiny party hat is slipping off its head. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures. The background is a simple, clean off-white with light pastel watercolor washes.
generatedPrompts.backCover: A minimalist and elegant back cover design. The majority of the panel is a clean, simple off-white background with a subtle paper texture. In the top-left corner, a small, tasteful watercolor splotch in a soft pastel teal, mimicking an organic paint bleed, provides a touch of color. The design is very sparse, with a focus on negative space, ensuring the bottom-right area is completely clear for branding or a QR code. Flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style with visible artistic brush strokes.
generatedPrompts.leftInterior: A subtle and decorative full-bleed background for the left interior of a greeting card. The entire panel features a soft, light pastel watercolor wash, blending gentle shades of lavender, blush pink, and pale yellow. A cascade of small, abstract confetti shapes drifts down from the top-right corner towards the bottom-left, rendered in the same soft watercolor style with visible brush strokes and organic paint bleeds. The composition is artistic and unobtrusive, providing visual interest without distracting from the main message area on the right. Flat 2D artwork with a subtle paper texture throughout.
generatedPrompts.rightInterior: A minimal and elegant background design focused on providing ample space for a handwritten message. The panel is primarily a clean off-white with a subtle paper texture. A single, delicate watercolor swatch of soft pastel gray is placed tastefully in the bottom-left corner, with a few tiny, abstract pastel confetti shapes appearing to scatter out from it. The decoration is minimal, confined to the corner to maximize writing space. The overall aesthetic is clean, artistic, and cohesive with the watercolor theme, featuring soft flowing colors and organic paint bleeds. Flat 2D artwork.
